         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><ab>
    <lb n="1"/>ἔτους <num value="4">δ</num> Μεσορὴ <num value="2">β</num> <expan>μ<ex>εμετρήκασιν</ex></expan> εἰς τὸν ἐν Διὸς <expan>πόλ<ex>ει</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="2"/>τῆι <expan>μ<ex>εγάλῃ</ex></expan> <expan>θη<ex>σαυρὸν</ex></expan> <app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 2.1.73">εἰς τὸ <num value="1/2">𐅵</num> <expan><ex>ἀρτάβης</ex></expan></lem><rdg><abbr>ἐ<unclear>πι</unclear>κ</abbr></rdg></app> <num value="4">δ</num> <expan><ex>ἔτους</ex></expan> <app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 2.1.73"><expan>Πετεήσιο<ex>ς</ex></expan></lem><rdg><expan>Πετεψάιο<ex>ς</ex></expan></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="3"/>Ψενοσίριος καὶ οἱ <expan>μέ<ex>τοχοι</ex></expan> <expan><ex>πυροῦ</ex></expan> δίμοιρον 

    <lb n="4"/><expan><ex>γίνεται</ex></expan> <expan><ex>πυροῦ</ex></expan> <num value="2/3">𐅷</num>. </ab></div>
